# dashboard-title.txt — a short project label shown in the harness dashboard's header (next to the
# gear icon) and browser tab, so you can tell multiple open dashboards apart when running the harness
# on more than one project. Copy to `dashboard-title.txt` (drop the .example) to activate. Blank lines
# and #-comments are ignored; the first remaining line is used verbatim — keep it short, since it's
# the browser tab title too. No file (or an empty one) → the dashboard just shows "Harness".
#
# Example:
# Storefront API
